{"tid":297762,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【屢敗屢戰】暑期捉曱甴大作戰！今次試吓用針筒毒餌？","createTime":"2017-06-25T17:34:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T16:03:25.000Z","uid":35370,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28f6c1b49c9ee20a9cec8daaf356b2c2af11fffd","tid":297762,"uid":35370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:34:56.000Z","msg":"是咁的，對上一次捉曱甴我試咗紅酒捉曱甴大法<br />\n仲邀請各位巴絲見証，詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/24915/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/24915/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但好遺憾地，戰略失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原因係呢種方法只係對唔識飛嘅美國強有用<br />\n而我屋企係一屋德國強，細細隻識飛嘅<br />\n佢哋唔會中計浸死自己<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後，我又試過用曱甴屋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/640pix/20040923/Article_LiveMag/23fj3pzok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20040923%2FArticle_LiveMag%2F23fj3pzok.jpg&h=5e1c2296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDLLM，點知又係捉班曱甴唔住<br />\n完全冇用，大家可以慳返筆錢唔駛買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n於是，今日就試吓用親戚同事推薦嘅針筒毒餌<br />\n<img src=\"http://i63.tinypic.com/o8x8br.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi63.tinypic.com%2Fo8x8br.png&h=99efc357&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖中隻手係五十幾歲老女人嘅，唔好亂嚟）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/n4cb0gy5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fn4cb0gy5&h=eed997b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吱出嚟，成pat芥辣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後就係等成果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有消息我再上嚟匯報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"035aa4cd52f2ef6d3552c8cec2932d10551d9613","tid":297762,"uid":14912,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:35:59.000Z","msg":"又要打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a4f230dc17f4a45b0aa44283e9de93c7d83d4f","tid":297762,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:37:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又要打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022e6bc1262d544e0b5ff7da59c1f07c631b44c9","tid":297762,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:37:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又要打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食得咁偏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ca946e64148c96e00a24fe601d4c4c5889dfc7","tid":297762,"uid":10815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:50:28.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"c438fdc878e3b2828074fbc9326e779ce0f08ab8","tid":297762,"uid":8364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:59:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又要打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黎哥哥到，我俾d好野你算啦"},{"pid":"d24fa51797a343bd7331c9a49841246816e16a77","tid":297762,"uid":112467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:59:30.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"5dcb110a34bc170c5b6c04cab100bf8298075f2e","tid":297762,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T18:01:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又要打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黎哥哥到，我俾d好野你算啦</blockquote><br />\n一個比一個偏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f87db3f5fafff148ba4965954bc541e8cda30b55","tid":297762,"uid":66283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T18:03:56.000Z","msg":"不嬲屋企都開類似嘅藥，係同d滅蟲佬買嘅，80支<img src=\"/assets/faces/